# Sky Auger Internal SpaceWire Architecture

This document describes the actual internal implementation of the SpaceWire subsystem
within the Earendel/sw repository (`bridge/` module). It is specific to the Sky Auger /
ORTHUS project and should be used alongside the API references when writing or reviewing
flight-bound code.

---

## Top-Level Module Structure

```
bridge/
├── source/
│   ├── spw/           # SpaceWire channel management
│   │   └── spw_channel.c
│   ├── uio/           # Userspace I/O subsystem (mediates SPW ↔ application)
│   │   ├── uio_channel.c
